<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,151,1187]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,555,1018,1043]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
Distribution in 
<collectingRegion box="[384,550,1018,1043]" country="Brazil" name="Minas Gerais" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Minas Gerais</collectingRegion>
:
</emphasis>
The species appears to be associated to forest environments in eastern 
<collectingCountry box="[1360,1431,1018,1043]" name="Brazil" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Brazil</collectingCountry>
, with its westernmost record in the ecotone between the Cerrado (savanna) and the inland seasonal forests of the Atlantic Forest, in 
<collectingRegion box="[361,511,1090,1115]" country="Brazil" name="Minas Gerais" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Minas Gerais</collectingRegion>
state, and the northernmost record in an isolated forest refuge in 
<collectingRegion box="[1242,1326,1090,1115]" country="Brazil" name="Paraiba" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Paraíba</collectingRegion>
state (see “Habitat”, above).
</paragraph>
